short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Improvements for Jenkins Blue Ocean via Chrome extension

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Jenkins Blue Ocean UI has few features that might not be optimal for all users. This extension is trying to improve the user experience by providing extra functionality or by disabling some of the functionality. Currently supported modules are:
- Pipeline status to favicon.
- Pipeline log auto collapse.
